Odey Asset Management Hires Dipankar Shewaram to Work Alongside Tim Bond in Managing the Odey Odyssey Fund
Oct 18 16
Odey Asset Management has hired Dipankar Shewaram to work alongside Tim Bond in managing the Odey Odyssey fund. Shewaram joins the investment team from Glendevon King Asset Management, where he had been working as a strategic investment advisor. Prior to this, Shewaram worked at BlueBay Asset Management as a portfolio manager, and Western Asset Management as the head of non-US credit.


