                            Odey Wealth Management (C.I.) Ltd., Odey Wealth Management (UK) Ltd., Odey Asset Management Group Ltd., Odey Asset Management LLP, ICP Holdings Ltd., Barings Bank, ICP Holdings Ltd., Magallanes Value Investors SA SGIIC, ICP General Partner Ltd..
            





